data.description: HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER TERRACES  GATED COMMUNITY IN SUMMERLIN, ADJACENT TO THE TCP GOLF COURSE. ENTIRE UNIT FRESHLY PAINTED, KITCHEN CABINETS PAINTED WITH NEW HARDWARE. VERY OPEN FLOOR PLAN, SEPARATE DINING ROOM. LARGE MASTER BEDROOM, MASTER BATH HAS DOUBLE SINKS, SHOWER/TUB COMBINATION.  LAUNDRY ROOM WITH WASHER AND DRYER, ONE ATTACHED GARAGE WITH DIRECT UNIT ENTRY, SECOND GARAGE DETACHED. SPECTACULAR VIEW OF COMM POOL AND SPA.  1 STORY/2ND FLOOR UNIT.
